---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | Kesem Records">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Kesem Records is a sound design and music production studio founded by
        DoGBeaT. We specialize in crafting sonic experiences that bridge the gap
        between technology and emotion.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our work spans film scoring, electronic music production, sound design
        for visual media, and the development of custom audio tools. Every
        project begins with listening and ends with something worth hearing.
      </p>

      <h2>Approach</h2>
      <p>
        We believe in precision without sterility. Each sound is intentional,
        each silence meaningful. Our process combines analog warmth with digital
        precision, vintage character with modern clarity.
      </p>

      <h2>Tools & Technology</h2>
      <p>
        Beyond music production, we develop custom instruments, processing
        chains, and audio utilities. Our tools are built by producers, for
        producers &mdash; practical solutions born from real studio needs.
      </p>

      <h2>DoGBeaT</h2>
      <p>
        Producer, sound designer, and the creative force behind Kesem Records.
        With years of experience across genres and media, DoGBeaT brings a
        distinctive sonic signature to every project &mdash; raw, precise, and
        unmistakably intentional.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
